    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all restoration fans and DIY mechanics! This vehicle is ready for its next chapter and is the perfect project for someone looking to bring a classic back to life. While it's currently in poor condition and will need significant work to get back on the road, it offers a fantastic foundation or a wealth of valuable parts for your next build. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own!",
